## 10. Risk Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|------------|
| Context becomes God object | High | Strict schema; split into sub-contexts if needed |
| Performance overhead > 2ms | High | Lazy initialization; object pooling; Cython optimization |
| Migration breaks existing plugins | High | Dual access pattern; comprehensive testing; gradual deprecation |
| Schema changes break compatibility | Medium | Versioned schema; migration scripts; backward compatibility |
| Memory leaks in context | Medium | Reference counting; weak references for large objects |

